<recipe>
<title>
Sticky Nut Recipe
</title>
<details>
AUTHOR: I Heart Eating
PREP TIME: 5 minutes
COOK TIME: 11 minutes
TOTAL TIME: 16 minutes
COURSE: Dessert
CUISINE: American
KEYWORD: nuts
SERVINGS: 12 servings
</details>
<ingredients>
1/2 c. real maple syrup
1/2 c. agave nectar
1/2 tsp. vanilla extract
1/4 c. cold butter
Pinch of salt
1 1/2 c. pecan or walnut pieces
</ingredients>
<instructions>
Add all of the ingredients except the nuts to a heavy saucepan.
Heat over medium heat until boiling.
Stir to combine.
Add nuts, and continue cooking for 1 more minute.
Let cool before using. The syrup will thicken as it cools.
</instructions>
</recipe>
